y%20(BOCA)%20of%20the%20PDA%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20instead%20of%20acting%20against%20the%20hotelier%2C%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%20amended%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20building%20permission%2C%20and%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20was%20shunted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20sent%20a%20detailed%20questionnaire%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20(J%26amp%3BK)%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%2C%20seeking%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20committed%20by%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20then-PDA%20CEO.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20documents%20and%20sources%2C%20permission%20for%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20construction%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20in%20its%2013th%20meeting%20on%20October%206%20and%20October%2025%20last%20year.%20Under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20permission%20letter%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20owner%20was%20directed%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20first%20hut%20in%20first%20stage%20of%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20%5Bthe%5D%20completion%20of%20one%20hut%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20second%20%5Bhut%5D%20shall%20be%20started%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20states%20while%20stressing%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cregeneration%20of%20the%20natural%20landscape%E2%80%9D%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20environment%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Lidder%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665531%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20under-construction%20hotel%20is%20situated%20barely%20100%20metres%20from%20one%20of%20the%20key%20tributaries%20of%20the%20Lidder%20river%20in%20Pahalgam.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel%20started%20in%20April%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20PDA%20CEO%2C%20a%20local%20activist%20named%20Mudasir%20Ahmed%20alleged%20that%20the%20owner%20had%20violated%20the%20terms%20of%20permission.%20The%20letter%20states%20that%20the%20hotel%20owner%20had%20used%20%E2%80%9Cnon-permissible%20machinery%20to%20change%20the%20topography%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20eco-fragile%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20locals%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20PDA%2C%20seeking%20verification%20of%20the%20revenue%20records%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20hotel%20may%20be%20coming%20up%20on%20a%20flood%20water%20channel%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20government%20but%20under%20the%20care%20of%20locals%2C%20and%20not%20proprietary%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20case%20under%20observance%20%5Bsic%5D%20needs%20official%20probe%20to%20know%20the%20reality%20currently%20dancing%20behind%20the%20bars%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20has%20been%20marked%20to%20the%20Kashmir%20divisional%20commissioner%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20served%20as%20a%20discharge%20canal%20for%20cloudbursts%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Pahalgam%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20wishing%20anonymity%20said%2C%20while%20demanding%C2%A0%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20fudging%20of%20revenue%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20administration%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20this%20claim%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20hotel%20was%20coming%20up%20on%20proprietary%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20not%20immediately%20verify%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20a%20PDA%20team%20visited%20the%20site%20in%20May%20and%20found%20that%20the%20hotel%20was%20being%20built%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20terms%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20BOCA.%20Following%20the%20visit%2C%20the%20then-CEO%2C%20Syed%20Sajad%20Qadri%2C%20a%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Administrative%20Service%20officer%2C%20flagged%20the%20violations%20to%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%2C%20Syeed%20Fakhrudin%20Hamid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20property%20owner%20on%20May%2018%2C%20the%20assistant%20executive%20engineer%20of%20the%20PDA%20stated%20that%20during%20the%20site%20inspection%2C%20it%20was%20noted%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20you%20have%20violated%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20the%20permission%20%E2%80%A6%20by%20starting%20construction%20work%20of%20all%20three%20huts%20altogether%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20%5Ba%5D%20column-type%20structure%20instead%20of%20%5Ba%5D%20load-bearing%20structure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDA%20notice%20warned%20the%20hotel%20owner%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20the%20construction%20work%20immediately%20and%20rectify%20the%20deviation%20within%20two%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%20of%20failure%20the%20same%20shall%20be%20demolished%20by%20the%20Pahalgam%20Development%20Authority%20at%20your%20risk%20and%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PDA%20notice%2C%20which%20was%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20material%20used%20by%20the%20hotelier%20has%20been%20dumped%20on%20the%20pristine%20meadows%2C%20damaging%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20area.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%2C%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20wrote%20to%20Anantnag%20DC%20Fakhrudin%20Hamid%20seeking%20permission%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20buildings%20%E2%80%9Cin%20case%20the%20applicant%20fails%20to%20follow%20the%20conditions%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20permission%20letter.%E2%80%9D%20The%20letter%20came%20after%20an%20%E2%80%9Cemergency%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20was%20called%20by%20the%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states%20that%20the%20building%20plan%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20which%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20(the%20only%20authority%20empowered%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20to%20building%20plans)%2C%20was%20allegedly%20changed%20on%20the%20verbal%20directions%20of%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Bchange%20in%20building%20plan%5D%20needs%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20as%20per%20the%20Development%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20then-PDA%20CEO%20notes%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20law%20which%20governs%20the%20PDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20BOCA%20didn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20to%20approve%20the%20change%20in%20the%20terms%20of%20permission%20granted%20to%20the%20hotel%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmir-respect-national-symbols-fear%5C%22%3EIn%20Kashmir%2C%20Respect%20for%20National%20Symbols%20Cannot%20Be%20Commanded%20By%20Fear%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20instead%20of%20acting%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20officer%2C%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20shunted%20out%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20on%20May%2020%20to%20the%20general%20administration%20department%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20a%20punishment%20posting%2C%20while%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20post%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%20denied%20that%20the%20administration%20had%20resorted%20to%20irregularities%20to%20allow%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel.%20However%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20explain%20the%20reason%20for%20amending%20the%20BOCA%E2%80%99s%20permission%20within%20six%20months%20of%20its%20approval%2C%20and%20directed%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20incumbent%20PDA%20CEO%2C%20Tariq%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20on%20the%20matter%20because%20I%20was%20not%20posted%20in%20Pahalgam%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hussain%20said%2C%20while%20refusing%20to%20elaborate%20on%20the%20action%20taken%20against%20the%20hotel%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20has%20banned%20construction%20in%20Pahalgam%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2