99s%20GDP.%20It%E2%80%99s%20deliberately%20light-weight%2C%20blindingly%20glossy%2C%20unhealthily%20sweet%20and%20yet%20witty%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20Randhawa%20(Ranveer%20Singh)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20scion%20of%20the%20Randhawa%20family%E2%80%99s%20Dhanlaxmi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eladdoo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20empire%2C%20named%20after%20and%20built%20by%20his%20grandmother%20(Jaya%20Bachchan)%20%E2%80%93%20opens%20the%20film%20with%20a%20charm-offensive%20voiceover%2C%20introducing%20his%20family%20members.%20Bachchan%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20a%20lifetime%20playing%20stoic%2C%20meek%20characters%2C%20is%20refreshingly%20cast%20as%20the%20acidic%20matriarch%20of%20the%20Randhawa%20household.%20Motivated%20by%20her%20quest%20for%20wealth%2C%20and%20disappointed%20by%20her%20husband%20Kanwal%E2%80%99s%20(Dharmendra)%20artistic%20pursuits%2C%20she%20names%20her%20son%2C%20Tijori%20(Aamir%20Bashir)%20and%20rules%20%E2%80%98Randhawa%20paradise%E2%80%99%20(hilariously%20modelled%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20White%20House)%20with%20an%20iron%20fist.%20One%20day%20Kanwal%2C%20who%20after%20an%20accident%20which%20makes%20him%20wheelchair-bound%20and%20suffering%20irregular%20bouts%20of%20amnesia%2C%20starts%20uttering%20a%20name%20%E2%80%98Jamini%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20looks%20into%20it.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20one%20Google%20search%20later%2C%20he%20finds%20out%20that%20the%20woman%20he%E2%80%99s%20referring%20to%20is%20related%20to%20a%20primetime%20news%20anchor%2C%20Rani%20Chatterjee%20(Alia%20Bhatt).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20two%20comets%20colliding%20into%20one%20another%2C%20Rocky%20and%20Rani%20meet%2C%20but%20initially%20to%20help%20complete%20the%20love%20story%20of%20Kanwal%20and%20Jamini%20(Shabana%20Azmi)%2C%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20grandmother.%20Seeing%20Rocky%E2%