E2%80%99%20of%20acting.%20There%E2%80%99s%20something%20sincere%20about%20them%20as%20frail%2C%20longing%20elders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20and%20Rani%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20title%20of%20the%20film%20suggests%20%E2%80%93%20are%20destined%20to%20fall%20in%20love.%20However%2C%20not%20before%20a%20social%20experiment%20that%20includes%20them%20living%20with%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20families%20for%20three%20months%2C%20so%20as%20to%20overcome%20the%20significant%20gap%20in%20their%20cultural%20upbringing.%20Johar%2C%20never%20shying%20away%20from%20a%20joke%20to%20mine%20the%20cultural%20differences%2C%20makes%20a%20joke%20about%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98Dadaji%E2%80%99%20by%20Rocky.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20scene%20Tota%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20playing%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20father%20Chandan%2C%20a%20Kathak%20dancer%20by%20vocation%20%E2%80%94%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20doing%20hand%20movements%20while%20being%20seated%20in%20Rocky%E2%80%99s%20living%20room%2C%20stressing%20upon%20how%20culturally%20refined%20he%20is.%20Seen%20through%20a%20comical%20lens%2C%20it%20does%20disservice%20to%20Roy%20Chowdhury%E2%80%99s%20otherwise%20superbly%20calibrated%20performance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20underneath%20all%20this%20fluff%20and%20humour%20also%20lies%20some%20pointed%20(and%20some%20patronising)%20social%20commentary.%20Johar%20touches%20upon%20the%20casual%20sexism%20in%20the%20Randhawa%20family%2C%20even%20with%20the%20women%20singing%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpLyDTEw3Z4%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaanto%20se%20kheech%20ke%20yeh%20aanchal%2C%20tod%20ke%20bandhan%2C%20baandhi%20payal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20front%20of%20their%20oppressors.%20When%20has%20Johar%20ever%20been%20known%20for%20half-measures%3F%20Rocky%20is%20reformed%20from%20his%20toxic%20masculinity%20by%20embracing%20kathak%20because%20of%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20and%20the%20Chatterjees%20are%20called%20out%20for%20their%20snootiness%20and%20superiority%20complex%20later%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20progressive%20posturing%20%E2%80%93%20possibly%20inspired%20by%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%E2%80%99s%20genre%20of%20films%20%E2%80%94%20is%20delivered%20well%2C%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20painful%20detours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Churni%20Ganguly%2C%20playing%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20goes%20on%20a%20lengthy%20tirade%20when%20Rocky%20is%20embarrassed%20to%20go%20lingerie%20shopping%20with%20her.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20scene%20between%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Alia%20Bhatt%20%E2%80%93%20eerily%20similar%20to%20a%20scene%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECrazy%20Rich%20Asians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2018)%20where%20Michelle%20Yeoh%20tells%20Constance%20Wu%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20will%20never%20be%20enough%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20that%20ends%20with%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20character%20saying%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhela%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ehobe%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20game%20is%20on).%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20the%20oddest%20bit%20of%20appropriation%20from%20Bengal%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaran%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Ki%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rests%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20its%20two%20excellent%20leads.%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20miss%20a%20beat%20playing%20a%20%E2%80%9890s%20Govinda%E2%80%93meets%E2%80%93Bittu%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baraat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efool%20%E2%80%93%20is%20able%20to%20turn%20his%20bratty%20character%20into%20someone%20earnest%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhatt%2C%20looking%20distressingly%20false%20in%20th