3.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewithheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20incentives%20claimed%20by%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%20Ltd%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20scheme%20totalling%20Rs%20900%20crore%20on%20the%20sales%20of%20about%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%2C%20citing%20invoicing%20discrepancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20in%20advanced%20stage%20of%20discussions%20with%20Government%20of%20India%20on%20the%20incentive%20payout.%20Samsung%20is%20a%20committed%20partner%20of%20India%20for%20over%2026%20years.%20As%20the%20leading%20smartphone%20player%2C%20we%20have%20been%20working%20closely%20with%20various%20stakeholders%20to%20make%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Samsung%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffreebies-pli-scheme-manufacturing%5C%22%3EAre%20Government%20Freebies%20Under%20PLI%20Scheme%20Truly%20Necessary%20to%20Enhance%20Manufacturing%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20loopholes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20PLI%20scheme%20is%20one%20of%20the%20initiatives%20under%20the%20flagship%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20Abhiyaan.%20The%20scheme%20is%20aimed%20at%20creating%20more%20jobs%2C%20attracting%20greater%20investments%2C%20reducing%20imports%2C%20and%20making%20India%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20is%20being%20touted%20as%20the%20panacea%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20problems%2C%20several%20loopholes%20in%20the%20scheme%20are%20raising%20concerns%20over%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20May%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fcons-products%2Felectronics%2Findia-surpasses-rs-85000-cr-worth-mobile-phone-exports-in-fy23%2Farticleshow%2F99334570.cms%5C%22%3Esurpassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2410%20billion%20(Rs%2082%2C000%20crore)%20worth%20smartphone%20exports%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202023%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20in%20exports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretail.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fconsumer-durables-and-information-technology%2Fmobiles%2Findian-smartphone-export-likely-crossed-over-rs-82000-crore-in-fy-2022-2023%2F99204073%5C%22%3Ewas%20attributed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20PLI%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Raghuram%20Rajan%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findias-mobile-phone-exports-driven-by-assembly-rather-than-domestic-manufacturing-raghuram-rajan%5C%22%3Eopined%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20boom%20in%20mobile%20phone%20exports%20might%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20concern%20as%20the%20growth%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20back%20of%20assembly%20rather%20than%20genuine%20manufacturing%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20key%20deficiency%20of%20the%20scheme%20is%20that%20the%20subsidy%20is%20paid%20only%20for%20finishing%20the%20phone%20in%20India%2C%20not%20on%20how%20much%20value%20is%20added%20by%20manufacturing%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20matters!%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20very%20little%20apart%20from%20assembly%20is%20done%20in%20India%2C%20though%20manufacturers%20claim%20they%20intend%20to%20do%20more%20in%20future.%20So%20India%20still%20imports%20much%20of%20what%20goes%20into%20the%20mobile%20phone%2C%20and%20when%20we%20correct%20for%20that%2C%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20maintain%20that%20net%20exports%20have%20gone%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20retired%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20professor%20Arun%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpli-scheme-subsidies-demand-shortage-jobs%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20despite%20a%20promise%20of%20increased%20profits%2C%