E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20justify%20their%20continuous%20detention%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBooked%20under%20the%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%2C%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%20last%20year.%20Their%20bail%20applications%20had%20earlier%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20special%20NIA%20court%20and%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court.%20Senior%20lawyers%20Rebecca%20John%20and%20R.%20Basant%20had%20highlighted%20the%20inordinate%20delay%20in%20the%20commencement%20of%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20grounds%20in%20the%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20court%20today%2C%20while%20granting%20them%20bail%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20fact%20that%20almost%20five%20years%20have%20lapsed%20since%20they%20(Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira)%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%E2%80%A6%20the%20appellants%20have%20made%20out%20a%20case%20for%20granting%20of%20bail.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lawyers%20had%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%20against%20the%20arrested%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20registered%20by%20the%20Pune%20police%20in%20January%202018%20and%20later%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20since%20the%20very%20start.%20While%20the%20state%20had%20initially%20claimed%20that%2016%20persons%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20including%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20%E2%80%93%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20%E2%80%9Cprovoking%E2%80%9D%20the%20gathered%20crowd%20at%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20with%20their%20speeches%20and%20triggering%20violence%20on%20the%20200th-anniversary%20celebration%20of%20the%20battle%20of%20Bhima%20Koregaon%2C%20they%20were%20later%20accused%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Curban%20Naxals%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20claims%20of%20their%20alleged%20association%20with%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20organisation%20is%20based%20on%20purported%20emails%20and%20other%20evidence%20allegedly%20retrieved%20from%20the%20electronic%20devices%20belonging%20to%20the%20accused.%20These%20claims%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20challenged%20by%20many%20independent%20forensic%20organisations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20investigation%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felgar-parishad-case-surveillance-pegasus%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20partner%20news%20organisations%20revealed%20that%20at%20least%20nine%20numbers%20belonged%20to%20eight%20activists%2C%20lawyers%20and%20academics%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20were%20either%20persons%20of%20interest%20or%20forensically%20identified%20as%20having%20been%20targeted%20by%20clients%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware.%20A%20Massachusetts-based%20digital%20forensics%20firm%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frona-wilson-pegasus-iphone-arsenal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArsenal%20Consulting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20later%20confirmed%20at%20least%20one%20phone%20%E2%80%93%20belonging%20to%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist%20Rona%20Wilson%20%E2%80%93%20was%20definitely%20infected%20by%20the%20malicious%20spyware.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%20are%20Sudhir%20Dhawale%2C%20a%20writer%20and%20Mumbai-based%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%3B%20Mahesh%20Raut%2C%20a%20young%20activist%20from%20Gadchiroli%20who%20worked%20on%20displacement%3B%20Shoma%20Sen%2C%20who%20had%20been%20head%20of%20the%20English%20literature%20department%20at%20Nagpur%20University%3B%20advocates%20Arun%20Ferreira%20and%20Sudha%20Bharadwaj%3B%20writer%20Varavara