ely%20sent%20an%20email%20to%20the%20travel%20agency%20I%20was%20working%20at%20in%20Australia%20to%20tell%20them%20I%20was%20resigning.%20I%20loved%20working%20there%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20the%20thought%20of%20staying%20in%20Europe%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enjoyed%20cooking%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20crew-chef%20position.%20In%20the%20winter%20months%2C%20the%20head%20chef%20leaves%20the%20yacht%20because%20the%20guests%20aren't%20there%2C%20but%20someone%20still%20needs%20to%20cook%20for%20the%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20apply%20for%20the%20job%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20first%20sit%20for%20a%20fire-and-water%20safety%20exam%20and%20have%20a%20medical%20exam%20to%20see%20that%20I%20was%20fit%20enough%20for%20the%20position.%20Because%20I%20was%20in%20Palma%2C%20in%20Mallorca%2C%20Spain%2C%20a%20hub%20for%20superyachts%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20my%20certifications%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20gave%20out%20my%20CV%20to%20a%20few%20people%20at%20a%20marina%2C%20and%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20yacht%20owned%20by%20the%20Formula%201%20champion%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ff1-champion-and-aviation-entrepreneur-niki-lauda-dies-at-70-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENiki%20Lauda%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20me%20a%20temporary%20crew-chef%20job%20for%20that%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20worked%20on%2020%20different%20superyachts%20in%20Asia%2C%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20in%20the%20Mediterranean.%20Here's%20what%20it's%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20have%20any%20chef's%20qualifications%20for%20my%20first%20two%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%2C%20I%20wasn't%20worried%20about%20cooking%20spaghetti%20Bolognese%20for%20the%20crew%2C%20but%20I%20panicked%20when%20the%20captain%20said%20I'd%20need%20to%20cook%20for%20the%20owner%20because%20the%20Michelin-trained%20chef%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20board%20the%20boat%20in%20time%20for%20his%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20being%20so%20nervous%2C%20but%20they%20must've%20liked%20the%20sushi%20platter%20I%20made%20because%20I%20managed%20to%20get%20my%20next%20boat%20job%20thanks%20to%20their%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20expand%20my%20skill%20set%2C%20so%20I%20took%20a%20ship's%20chef-certification%20course%20in%20France%2C%20which%20costs%20around%20%241%2C200.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fleiths.com%2Fprofessional-courses%2Fassessment-in-marine-cookery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeiths%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20London%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bluewateryachting.com%2Ftraining-course%2Fship-s-cook-assessment-168%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluewater%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Florida%20and%20Monaco%20also%20now%20offer%20this%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20taken%20temporary%20jobs%20in%20places%20such%20as%20Seychelles%20and%20Bali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20worked%20on%20one%20superyacht%20for%202-and-%C2%BD%20years%2C%20where%20we%20would%20cross%20the%20Atlantic%20each%20season.%20I've%20cooked%20for%20stars%20including%20Pharrell%20Williams%2C%20politicians%2C%20and%20members%20of%20royalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20yachts%20I've%20worked%20on%20have%20personal%20submarines%2C%20helipads%2C%20and%20spas.%20They%20can%20have%20up%20to%2012%20hotel-style%20suites%2C%20so%20the%20owners%20will%20often%20bring%20multiple%20guests%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20yacht%20that%20had%20a%20full%20editing%20suite%2C%20which%20a%20National%20Geographic%20documentarian%20used%20to%20edit%20a%20video%20he'd%20made%20of%20the%20owners%20scuba%20diving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20now%20sailed%20into%20many%20glamorous%20marinas%2C%20but%20the%20one%20port%20that%20blew%20me%20away%20was%20in%20Malta.%20The%20galley%20of%20the%20boat%20had%20huge%20windows%2C%20so%20we%20could%20see%20big%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B-style%20castles%20on%20the%20hilltop%20as%20we%20arrived.%20It%20looked%20like%20a%20port%20you%20might%20have%20entered%20in%20the%20olden%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20grand%20harbor%20marina%20in%20Malta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c2a986048ff200190be563%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20grand%20harbor%20marina%20in%20Malta.%3Cp%3ELordHenriVoton%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20day%20usually%20starts%20at%206%20a.m.%20when%20I%20fire%20up%20the%20ovens%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20prep%20fruit%20plates%20and%20pastries%20for%20breakfast%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20usually%20start%20receiving%20specific%20orders%20until%20the%20stewardesses%20tell%20me%20what%20the%20guests%20want%20to%20eat%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20any%20guests%20have%20any%20dietary%20issues%2C%20you%20must%20manage%20the%20galley%20so%20you%20don't%20cross%20contaminate.%20If%20you%20have%20guests%20with%20nut%20allergies%2C%20gluten%20allergies%2C%20or%20lactose%20intolerance%20on%20the%20same%20voyage%2C%20it%20can%20get%20quite%20hectic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20guests%20say%20they're%20going%20to%20eat%20onshore%2C%20I'm%20always%20prepared.%20Dinner%20reservations%20can%20fall%20through%2C%20or%20once%20they%20get%20to%20the%20restaurant%2C%20the%20yacht%20owners%20may%20decide%20the%20vibes%20are%20off%20and%20that%20they%20no%20longer%20want%20to%20eat%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20I'll%20get%20a%20call%20to%20make%20a%20midnight%20snack.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20group%20of%20younger%20people%20on%20the%20boat%20and%20they're%20going%20clubbing%20in%20Miami%2C%20I'll%20prep%20some%20wagyu-beef%20burgers%20for%20their%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20that%20I%20get%20requests%20for%20dishes%20with%20luxurious%20ingredients%2C%20such%20as%20fresh%20Alaskan-crab%20legs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20do%2C%20I'll%20arrange%20for%20them%20to%20be%20flown%20in%20from%20Alaska%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20yacht-chef%20WhatsApp%20groups%2C%20where%20fellow%20chefs%20will%20try%20to%20come%20to%20your%20aid%20if%20you%20need%20assistance.%20If%20I'm%20in%20St.%20Barts%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20I've%20run%20out%20of%20gluten-free%20flour%2C%20I%20can%20message%20other%20chefs%20in%20the%20area%20on%20WhatsApp%20to%20see%20who%20has%20any%20flour%2C%20and%20then%20I'll%20send%20the%20tender%20over%20to%20their%20boat%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20flour%20and%20bring%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20don't%20just%20cook%20for%20the%20owners%2C%20the%20guests%2C%20and%20the%20crew%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2C%20I%20cook%20for%20the%20owner's%20pets.%20On%20one%20boat%2C%20I%20would%20need%20to%20sous%20vide%20%E2%80%94%20a%20method%20of%20low-temperature%20cooking%20%E2%80%94%20chicken%20breasts%20every%20day%2C%20which%20I%20would%20then%20finely%20dice%20for%20the%20owner's%20two%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20tough%20days%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20a%20superyacht%20can%20be%20incredibly%20demanding.%20You'll%20only%20see%20the%20highlights%20of%20chef's%20days%20off%20on%20Instagram%2C%20and%20we%20never%20post%20about%20the%20tough%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20downside%20for%20me%20is%20being%20away%20from%20family%20and%20friends%20and%20missing%20birthdays%20or%20weddings.%20But%20I've%20also%20met%20some%20amazing%20crew%20on%20board%20yachts%2C%20including%20my%20new%20fianc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20take%20a%20selfie%20in%20front%20of%20a%20yacht%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c2a6c0cf0778001965721a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Cunningham%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Cunningham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20we%20had%20to%20do%20an%20Atlantic%20crossing%2C%20and%20the%20boat%20took%20an%20absolute%20beating.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20broken%20by%20the%20time%20we%20got%20to%20the%20other%20side%2C%20including%20a%20dining%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20I%20do%20have%20some%20downtime%2C%20I'll%20go%20ashore%20and%20take%20a%20local%20cooking%20class%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20always%20trying%20to%20learn.%20I've%20learned%20how%20to%20make%20pastries%20in%20Devon%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20I%20did%20a%20class%20in%20South%20Korea%20with%20the%20monk%20Jeong%20Kwan%20from%20%26quot%3BChef's%20Table%26quot%3B%20on%20Netflix.%20I'm%20now%20planning%20to%20do%20a%20big%20sushi%20course%20in%20Japan%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20also%20seek%20out%20the%20perfect%20ingredients%20when%20I'm%20in%20a%20port.%20I've%20bought%20pata-negra%20hams%20in%20Spain%20and%20jerk%20spice%20from%20Antigua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20full%20grocery%20cart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c2a61e048ff200190bdd74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECunningham's%20grocery%20haul%20for%20the%20yacht.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Cunningham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChefs%20can%20earn%20between%206%2C000%20and%2012%2C000%20euros%20a%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20working%20as%20a%20head%20chef%20on%20a%20busy%20charter%20yacht%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20between%206%2C000%20and%2012%2C000%20euros%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHead%20chefs%20are%20paid%20for%2012%20months%20and%20only%20work%20six.%20Tips%20can%20vary%20from%20nothing%20to%