software-developers-jobs-2023-4%5C%22%3Ewriting%20software%20code%20faster%20and%20easier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20churn%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbot-chatgpt-google-microsofty-lying-search-belief-2023-2%5C%22%3Efactual%20errors%20and%20lies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20developing%20a%20way%20to%20spot%20what%20is%20AI%20text%20versus%20human%20text%20is%20foundational.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt4-worse-on-some-tasks-chatgpt-2023-7%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20ChatGPT%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt4-ai-model-got-lazier-dumber-chatgpt-2023-7%5C%22%3EGPT-4%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20realized%20this%20a%20while%20ago.%20In%20January%2C%20it%20unveiled%20a%20%26quot%3Bclassifier%20to%20distinguish%20between%20text%20written%20by%20a%20human%20and%20text%20written%20by%20AIs%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20providers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20warned%20that%20it's%20impossible%20to%20reliably%20detect%20all%20AI-written%20text.%20However%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20good%20classifiers%20are%20important%20for%20tackling%20several%20problematic%20situations.%20Those%20include%20false%20claims%20that%20AI-generated%20text%20was%20written%20by%20a%20human%2C%20running%20automated%20misinformation%20campaigns%2C%20and%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20cheat%20on%20homework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20seven%20months%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-ai-detection-tool-shut-down-over-inaccuracy-2023-7%5C%22%3Ethe%20project%20was%20scrapped%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20of%20July%2020%2C%202023%2C%20the%20AI%20classifier%20is%20no%20longer%20available%20due%20to%20its%20low%20rate%20of%20accuracy%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fblog%2Fnew-ai-classifier-for-i