e%20initial%20filing%20period%20for%20those%20with%20selected%20registrations%20for%20FY%202024%20was%20from%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20through%20June%2030%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20is%20a%20non-immigrant%20visa%20that%20allows%20US%20companies%20to%20employ%20foreign%20workers%20in%20speciality%20occupations%20that%20require%20theoretical%20or%20technical%20expertise.%20Technology%20companies%20depend%20on%20it%20to%20hire%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%20each%20year%20from%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recently%20determined%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20select%20additional%20registrations%20to%20reach%20the%20FY%202024%20numerical%20allocations.%20Soon%2C%20we%20will%20select%20additional%20registrations%20from%20previously%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20using%20a%20random%20selection%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20USCIS%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20announce%20once%20we%20have%20completed%20this%20second%20selection%20process%20and%20have%20notified%20all%20prospective%20petitioners%20with%20selected%20registrations%20from%20this%20round%20of%20selection%20that%20they%20are%20eligible%20to%20file%20an%20H-1B%20cap-subject%20petition%20for%20the%20beneficiary%20named%20in%20the%20applicable%20selected%20registration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20with%20selected%20registrations%20will%20have%20their%20accounts%20updated%20to%20include%20a%20selection%20notice%2C%20which%20includes%20details%20of%20when%20and%20where%20to%20file%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mandated%20by%20Congress%2C%20USCIS%20can%20issue%20a%20maximum%20of%2065%2C000%20H-1B%20visas%20in%20a%20year.%20It%20can%20also%20issue%20another%2020%2C000%20H-1B%20visas%20to%20foreign%20students%20who%20have%20completed%20higher%20studies%20from%20a%20US%20university%20in%20Science%2C%20Technology%2C%20Engineering%20and%20