0Ed-Tech%20Startup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20has%20faced%20crises%20for%20months.%20Apart%20from%20the%20raid%20by%20financial%20crime-fighting%20agency%2C%20the%20once%20high-flying%20tutoring%20start-up%20failed%20to%20file%20its%20financial%20accounts%20on%20time.%20Several%20US-based%20investors%20have%20accused%20Byju's%20of%20hiding%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%2C%20prompting%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran's%20rise%20from%20a%20private%20tutor%20to%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20%2422%20billion%20company%20captivated%20global%20investors%2C%20including%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20Blackstone%20Inc%2C%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20foundation.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20he%20cornered%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20EdTech%20market%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20classrooms%20reopened%2C%20concerns%20about%20Byju's%20finances%20pricked%20at%20the%20firm's%20reputation.%20Investors%20questioned%20why%20Raveendran%20delayed%20hiring%20a%20chief%20financial%20officer%20for%20years%20and%20acquired%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20companies%20across%20the%20world%20at%20break-neck%20speed.%20Scores%20of%20employees%20have%20either%20left%20or%20been%20fired.%20Board%20members%20have%20resigned.%20And%20many%20teaching%20centres%20are%20nearly%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran's%20supporters%20attribute%20his%20missteps%20to%20the%20enthusiasm%20and%20naivete%20of%20an%20inexperienced%20founder%20who%20grew%20too%20quickly.%20But%20critics%20say%20he%20acted%20recklessly%20by%20withholding%20information%20about%20finances%20and%20failing%20to%20rigorously%20audit%20accounts.%20In%20India's%20start-up%20world%2C%20many%20see%20Byju's%20as%20the%20highest-profile%20example%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20a%20business%20scales%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20during%20a%20boom%20but%20fails%20to%20plan%20for%20a%20bust.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690529340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht