-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhave-identified-world-class-tech-partner-tying-up-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhave-identified-world-class-tech-partner-tying-up-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Can%20Bills%20Be%20Passed%20When...%5C%22%3A%20Congress%20Raises%20Query%20Ahead%20Of%20Delhi%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20on%20control%20of%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20up%20on%20Monday%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20which%20is%20fighting%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%20has%20questioned%20if%20bills%20can%20be%20passed%20when%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20is%20pending.%20In%20a%20tweet%20today%2C%20Congress's%20Manish%20Tewari%20cited%20a%20rule-book%20that%20suggests%20the%20opposite%2C%20and%20urged%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20to%20%26quot%3Bstart%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20no%20confidence%20motion%20without%20let%20or%20demur%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20travesty%20to%20pass%20bills%20when%20the%20no%20confidence%20is%20still%20pending%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20has%20indicated%20that%20traditionally%2C%20the%20date%20for%20debate%20and%20discussion%20is%20decided%20after%20consulting%20all%20parties%20and%20legislative%20business%20is%20not%20restricted%20in%20the%20intervening%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20Congress'%20objections%2C%20the%20Speaker%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20view%2C%20the%20time%20available%20to%20the%20House%20between%20leave%20being%20granted%20by%20the%20House%20and%20moving%20of%20the%20motion%20of%20no%20confidence%20can%20be%20gainfully%20utilised%20by%20the%20House%20in%20debates%20and%20discussion.%20The%20House%20would%20agree%20that%20it%20is%20our%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20legislate%20and%20raise%20issues%20of%20public%20importance.%20Rule%20198%20also%20does%20not%20bar%20taking%20up%20of%20any%20legislative%20or%20other%20matters%20of%20public%20importance%20after%20leave%20to%20moving%20a%20motion%20of%20no%20confidence%20has%20been%20granted%20by%20the%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20bills%20including%20the%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Bill%20were%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20Another%20was%20passed%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20after%20the%20Opposition's%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20Speaker.%20Pointing%20to%20the%20bills%2C%20Mr%20Tewari%20quoted%20from%20%26quot%3BPractice%20and%20Procedure%20of%20Parliament%26quot%3B%20by%20MN%20Kaul%20and%20SL%20Shakhdhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20leave%20of%20the%20house%20to%20the%20moving%20of%20a%20motion%20of%20'No%20confidence'%20has%20been%20granted%2C%20no%20substantive%20motion%20on%20Policy%20matters%20is%20to%20be%20brought%20before%20the%20house%20by%20the%20government%20till%20the%20motion%20of%20no%20confidence%20is%20not%20disposed%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20likely%20next%20week%20too%2C%20but%20well%20after%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20August%201%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20who%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20debate%20--%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20Maharashtra.%20So%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20can%20be%20discussed%2C%20answered%20and%20voted%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20will%20continue%20till%20August%2011%20and%20the%20government%20has%20a%20long%20list%20of%20bills%20it%20needs%20to%20push%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20controversial%20of%20them%20is%20the%20bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Ordinance%20that%20wrests%20power%20to%20control%20bureaucrats%20from%20the%20elected%20government%20of%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20Opposition%20is%20determined%20not%20to%20allow%20through%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20numbers%20indicate%20that%20the%20government%20is%20in%20a%20strong%20position.%20Today%2C%20the%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20declared%20that%20it%20would%20back%20the%20government%20both%20in%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20and%20the%20Delhi%20bill%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20numbers%20are%20stacked%20firmly%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20currently%20has%20238%20members%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20mark%20at%20120.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20105%20members%20and%20will%20have%20the%20support%20of%20nine%20YSRCP%20MPs.%20The%20ruling%20party%20is%20also%20confident%20of%20the%20support%20of%20five%20nominated%20and%20two%20independent%20MPs%2C%20which%20takes%20its%20numbers%20to%20121.%20Around%20105%20Opposition%20members%20are%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Ordinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690528800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F5sfdtv6s_lok-sabha-ani_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-bills-be-passed-when-congress-raises-query-ahead-of-delhi-bill-4247269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20on%20control%20of%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20likely%20to%20come%20up%20on%20Monday%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20is%20fighting%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%20has%20questioned%20if%20bills%20can%20be%20passed%20when%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20is%20pending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-bills-be-passed-when-congress-raises-query-ahead-of-delhi-bill-4247269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-n