rrific%20form%20he%20has%20been%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20of%20late.%20Seeing%20Surya%20struggle%20to%20score%20runs%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20once%20again%2C%20many%20fans%20sympathised%20with%20Samson%20who%20remains%20on%20the%20bench%20despite%20proving%20to%20be%20an%20asset%20in%20his%20recent%20outings%20in%20one-day%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Suryakumar%20incurred%20three%20consecutive%20ducks%20in%20his%20previous%20three%20ODIs%20--%20all%20against%20Australia%20--%20his%20last%206%20innings%20weren't%20great%20too.%20The%20middle-order%20batter's%20last%206%20scores%20read%2019%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200%2C%2014%20and%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20Samson's%20last%206%20scores%20are%3A%2036%2C%202*%2C%2030*%2C%2086*%2C%2015%20and%2043*.%20When%20compared%20to%20Suryakumar%2C%20Samson's%20average%20is%20also%20extremely%20high%2C%20at%2066%20in%2011%20matches.%20Surya%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20averages%2023.78%20in%2024%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20gonna%20field%20first%2C%20no%20particular%20reason%2C%20just%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20try%20a%20few%20different%20things%20and%20see%20where%20we%20are%20as%20a%20team.%20We%20want%20to%20head%20into%20the%20World%20Cup%20with%20a%20clear%20mindset.%20For%20us%2C%20the%20results%20are%20also%20important.%20At%20times%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20try%20out%20different%20players%20but%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20compromise%20on%20our%20results.%20All%20cricketers%20around%20the%20world%20who%20are%20playing%20all%20formats%20need%20to%20adapt%20well.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20can%20get%20what%20we%20want%20here.%20We%20have%20got%20four%20seamers%20and%20two%20spinners%2C%26quot%3B%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20had%20said%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20toss%2C%20suggesting%20he%20wants%20to%20try%20a%20few%20different%20things%20as%20the%20team%20prepares%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurya%2C%20who%20arguably%20remains%20the%20most%20fearsome%2