topic%20and%20requested%20that%20members%20discuss%20it%20under%20that%20rule.%20The%20Vice%20President%20then%20went%20on%20to%20speak%20about%20how%20the%20behavior%20of%20MPs%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20seen%20by%20the%20global%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Mr%20O'Brien%20stood%20up%2C%20thumped%20the%20desk%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20continue%20their%20efforts%20to%20introduce%20the%20motion%20that%20they%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20pass%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankar%20dubbed%20the%20Trinamool%20leader's%20actions%20as%20%26quot%3Btheatrics%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShow%20respect%20to%20the%20chair.%20Don't%20thump%20the%20desk.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20O'Brien%20continued%20with%20his%20sloganeering%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20adjourned%20the%20proceedings%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20120%20people%20and%20displaced%20thousands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690527780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjhe6h18g_dhankar-derek-_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-for-discussion-on-manipur-rajya-sabha-chairman-4247709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20today%20appealed%20to%20the%20House%20to%20rise%20above%20partisan%20interests%20and%20allow%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-for-discussion-on-manipur-rajya-sabha-chairman-4247709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-for-discussion-on