arrives-late-report-4247582%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Outdated%20Census%20Data%20Depriving%20Persons%20With%20Disabilities%20Access%20to%20Schemes%2C%20Grants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28103733%2Fimages.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20parliamentary%20committee%20has%20said%20that%20lack%20of%20updated%20Census%20data%20is%20depriving%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20access%20to%20grants%20and%20schemes%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fgovt-depriving-persons-with-disabilities-of-grants-schemes-due-to-no-census-parliamentary-panel-1241379.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20Census%2C%20there%20are%202.69%20crore%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%93%20a%20figure%20that%20is%2012%20years%20old.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20allocation%20of%20resources%2C%20determination%20of%20targets%20and%20assessment%20for%20trained%20professionals%20has%20fallen%20short%20since%20the%20projections%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Empowerment%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20under%20the%20social%20justice%20ministry%20still%20quote%20the%20old%20figure%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20committee%20took%20note%20of%20the%20number%20of%20unique%20ID%20cards%20allotted%20to%20those%20with%20disabilities.%20The%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20reply%20in%20the%20action%20taken%20report%20says%20that%20they%20have%20given%20these%20ID%20cards%20to%20keep%20a%20tab%20on%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20persons%20with%20disabilities.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20by%20the%20Department%E2%80%99s%20own%20admission%2C%20they%20have%20issued%2094.09%20lakh%20UDID%20cards%20so%20far%20whereas%20the%20PwD%20population%20even%2010%20years%20ago%20was%20more%20than%20double%20that%20number%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fgovt-depriving-persons-with-disabilities-of-grants-schemes-due-to-no-census-parliamentary-panel-1241379.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20made%20aware%20of%20surveys%20being%20conducted%20in%20certain%20states%20to%20determine%20the%20updated%20population%20of%20those%20with%20disabilities.%E2%80%9CThe%20Department%20can%20explore%20results%20of%20such%20surveys%20for%20gaining%20a%20fair%20understanding%20of%20their%20target%20population%20by%20adopting%20an%20out-of-the-box%20approach%2C%20because%20the%20next%20Census%20results%20may%20take%20a%20considerable%20time%20to%20come.%20The%20committee%20feels%20that%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20requirement%20to%20explore%20innovative%20solutions%20to%20this%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentioned%20the%20establishment%20of%20two%20new%20institutes%20and%20several%20Composite%20Regional%20Centres%20(CRC)%20to%20provide%20rehabilitation%20services%20to%20persons%20with%20disabilities.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Department%20also%20envisages%20to%20establish%20at%20least%20one%20CRC%20in%20each%20state%20irrespective%20of%20the%20size%20of%20the%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20added%20that%20the%20ministry%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20train%20Central%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(CPWD)%20and%20PWD%20officials%20on%20key%20accessibility%20features%20in%20buildings%20to%20sensitise%20them%20towards%20the%20importance%20of%20accessibility%20for%20all%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20said%20that%20since%20both%20these%20agencies%20are%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20carrying%20out%20public%20works%2C%20the%20training%20would%20inform%20their%20understanding%20of%20how%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20access%20public%20spaces%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20states%20should%20train%20their%20urban%20planners%2C%20architects%20and%20relevant%20execution%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690526711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28103733%2Fimages.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Foutdated-census-data-depriving-persons-with-disabilities-access-to-schemes-grants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%202011%20Census%2C%20there%20are%202.69%20crore%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%93%20a%20figure%20that%20is%2012%20years%20old.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Foutdated-census-data-depriving-persons-with-disabilities-access-to-schemes-grants%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Korea%20tunnel%20tragedy%3A%20Officials%20ignored%20multiple%20warnings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690526584000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1722D%2Fproduction%2F_130556749_be3456875c5f7606323a33c003a2a460c9799b69.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66333778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirty-six%20officials%20in%20South%20Korea%20are%20under%20investigation%20for%20failing%20to%20prevent%20the%20tragedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66333778%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66333778.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66333778.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AMD%20plans%20to%20invest%20%24400%20mn%20in%20India%20to%20expand%20R%26D%2C%20engineering%20operations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690526503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-stan