n%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20other%20nations%20are%20also%20clamoring%20to%20join%20the%20alliance%2C%20fueling%20western%20concerns%20the%20group%20is%20moving%20to%20become%20a%20counterweight%20to%20Washington%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%20wants%20to%20avoid%20expansion%20partly%20because%20of%20these%20worries%2C%20while%20India%20wants%20strict%20rules%20on%20how%20and%20when%20other%20nations%20could%20move%20closer%20to%20the%20group%2C%20without%20formally%20expanding%20it.%20Any%20decision%20will%20require%20consensus%20among%20the%20members%20who%20will%20meet%20Aug.%2022-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Brazil%20want%20to%20use%20the%20summit%20to%20discuss%20potentially%20bringing%20in%20additional%20countries%20with%20observer%20status%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%20South%20Africa%20supports%20discussing%20different%20membership%20options%20to%20accommodate%20this%2C%20but%20doesn't%20necessarily%20oppose%20expansion%2C%20two%20of%20the%20officials%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BRICS%20leaders%20meeting%20last%20year%20authorized%20the%20expansion%20of%20membership%2C%20adding%20more%20members%20to%20BRICS%20is%20the%20political%20consensus%20of%20the%20five%20BRICS%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20response%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20aims%20to%20showcase%20the%20bloc's%20goals%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20a%20serious%20political%20and%20economic%20force.%20The%20group%20has%20already%20discussed%20the%20potential%20establishment%20of%20a%20common%20currency%2C%20although%20significant%20progress%20toward%20that%20goal%20isn't%20expected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20of%20heightened%20tensions%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%2C%20and%20after%20South%20Africa%20fretted%20over%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20attendance.%20He'll%20participate%20virtually%20so%20South%20Africa%20doesn't%20have%20to%20execute%20an%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRICS%20members%20have%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20Group%20of%20Seven%20in%20blaming%20and%20sanctioning%20Russia%20over%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20although%20the%20New%20Development%20Bank%20started%20by%20BRICS%20froze%20Russian%20projects%20and%20Moscow%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20access%20dollars%20via%20the%20bloc's%20shared%20foreign%20currency%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20does%20not%20hold%20a%20firm%20position%20on%20expanding%20BRICS%20said%20Fyodor%20Lukyanov%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20and%20Defense%20Policy%2C%20which%20advises%20the%20Kremlin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20broadly%20in%20favor%20of%20BRICS%20expansion%2C%20but%20without%20any%20huge%20enthusiasm.%20It's%20following%20the%20others'%20lead.%20We%20won't%20block%20any%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormed%20officially%20in%202009-2010%2C%20the%20bloc%20has%20struggled%20to%20have%20the%20kind%20of%20geopolitical%20influence%20that%20matches%20its%20collective%20economic%20reach.%20Current%20BRICS%20members%20represent%20more%20than%2042%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20and%20account%20for%2023%25%20of%20global%20gross%20domestic%20product%20and%2018%25%20of%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDraft%20rules%20for%20admission%20to%20the%20group%20were%20drawn%20up%20after%20India's%20opposition%20to%20China's%20push%20for%20expansion%2C%20said%20two%20Indian%20officials.%20The%20guidelines%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20discussed%20and%20adopted%20during%20the%20leader's%20summit%20next%20month%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20put%20forward%20the%20idea%20that%20BRICS%20nations%20should%20look%20to%20emerging%20economies%20as%20well%20as%20democracies%20like%20Argentina%20and%20Nigeria%20if%20they%20want%20to%20expand%20the%20group%2C%20rather%20than%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20with%20its%20dynastic%20and%20autocratic%20rule%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officials%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20discussed%20issues%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20potential%20admission%20with%20the%20kingdom's%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammad%20bin%20Salman%20last%20month%2C%20the%20official%20said.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20India%20didn't%20comment.%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20government%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20BRICS%20would%20bolster%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed's%20attempts%20to%20diversify%20his%20nation's%20economy%2C%20an%20effort%20that%20has%20bought%20it%20closer%20to%20Russia%20and%20China%20in%20recent%20years.%20China%20is%20the%20kingdom's%20top%20oil%20customer%2C%20while%20it%20relies%20on%20relations%20with%20Russia%20for%20the%20OPEC%2B%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Saudis%20are%20having%20their%20Asian%20moment%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Saudi%20analyst%20Salman%20Al-Ansari%2C%20who%20said%20bilateral%20trade%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20exponentially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%20is%20working%20quietly%20to%20avoid%20direct%20confrontation%20in%20the%20BRICS%20bloc%20and%20resist%20pressure%20from%20China%20to%20make%20it%20an%20antagonistic%20body%20that%20challenges%20the%20G7%2C%20a%20Brazilian%20official%20said.%20China%20has%20reiterated%20the%20request%20for%20expansion%20at%20all%20preparatory%20meetings%2C%20including%20two%20last%20week%20which%20took%20place%20virtually%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil's%20proposal%20is%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bobserver%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpartner%20country%26quot%3B%20categories.%20New%20nations%20would%20first%20move%20through%20these%20categories%20before%20being%20considered%20for%20promotion%20to%20members%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20Brazil%20would%20support%20Indonesia%20beginning%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E--With%20assistance%20from%20Fahad%20Abuljadayel%20and%20Evelyn%20Yu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690522020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ftonvevho_brics-summit-ani-650_650x400_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-brazil-push-back-against-china-over-brics-expansion-4247221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20Brazil%20are%20pushing%20back%20against%20a%20Chinese%20bid%20to%20rapidly%20expand%20the%20BRICS%20group%20of%20emerging%20markets%20to%20grow%20its%20political%20clout%20and%20counter%20the%20US%2C%20officials%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-brazil-push-back-against-china-over-brics-expansion-4247221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-brazil-push-back-against-china-over-brics-expansion-4247221%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-brazil-push-back-against-china-over-brics-expansion-4247221%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prigozhin%3A%20Wagner%20boss%20spotted%20in%20Russia%20during%20Africa%20summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690521440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FFA4B%2Fproduction%2F_130557046_microsoftteams-image.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66333403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meanwhile%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20Russia%20was%20ready%20to%20send%20free%20grain%20exports%20to%20Africa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A322%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66333403%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66333403.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66333403.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arrest%20Warning%20For%20Congress%20Leader%20Over%20Lord%20Krishna%20%5C%22Love%20Jihad%5C%22%20Parallel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20equating%20Lord%20Krishna%20and%20Rukmini's%20relationship%20to%20so-called%20%26quot%3BLove%20Jihad%26quot%3B%20by%20Assam%20Pradesh%20Congress%20President%20Bhupen%20Kumar%20Borah%20is%20unfortunate%2C%20and%20the%20government%20will%20take%20action%20against%20him%20if%20a%20complaint%20is%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Borah%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20comment%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimanta-biswa-sarma-assam-triple-murder-a-case-of-love-jihad-4241902%5C%22%3Ethe%20recent%20triple%20murder%20in%20Assam's%20Golaghat%20was%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3BLove%20Jihad%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20term%20often%20used%20by%20right-wing%20politicians%20to%20allege%20a%20campaign%20by%20Muslim%20men%20to%20convert%20Hindu%20women%20by%20seducing%20them%2C%20courted%20controversy%20for%20calling%20the%20marriages%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%20and%20Rukmini%2C%20and%20Dhritarashtra%20and%20Gandhari%2C%20in%20the%20epic%20Mahabharata%2C%20%26quot%3BLove%20Jihad%26quot%3B%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20cross%20marriages%20going%20on%20since%20history%2C%20even%20among%20Kings%20since%20Mahabharata%20(sic).%20The%20main%20story%20in%20Mahabharata%20is%20that%20Gandhari's%20family%20didn't%20want%20her%20to%20marry%20Dhritarashtra.%20Bhisma%20Pitamah%20forced%20the%20marriage%20between%20them.%20Shakuni's%20brother%20was%20imprisoned%2C%20and%20later%20the%20mama%20took%20revenge.%20That%20is%20also%20love%20jihad.%20Gandhari's%20family%20objected%2C%20and%20as%20such%20she%20wore%20a%20cloth%20over%20her%20eyes.%20When%20Krishna%20came%20to%20take%20Rukmini%2C%20Arjun%20came%20in%20a%20different%20roop%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Borah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20condemned%20the%20Congress%20leader%20dragging%20Lord%20Krishna%20into%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20against%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20it%20is%20against%20Hindu%20Dharma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20requests%20Mr%20Borah%20not%20to%20bring%20up%20Lord%20Krishna%20in%20the%20controversy%20like%20%26quot%3Bwe%20shouldn't%20drag%20Hajrat%20Mohammad%20or%20Jesus%20Christ%26quot%3B%20into%20any%20religious%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecondly%2C%20what%20is%20love%20jihad%3F%20When%20a%20girl%20is%20married%20by%20false%20identity%20and%20is%20forced%20to%20change%20her%20religion%20after%20marriage.%20Lord%20Krishna%20never%20asked%20Rukmini%20to%20change%20her%20religion.%20If%20someone%20files%20a%20case%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20arrest%20the%20person%20who%20has%20said%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Mr%20Borah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E25-year-old%20Nazibur%20Rahman%20Bora%20on%20Wednesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-lockdown-love-story-ended-in-grisly-triple-murder-in-assam-4240391%5C%22%3Emurdered%20his%2024-year-old%20wife%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sanghamitra%20Ghosh%2C%20and%20her%20parents%2C%20before%20surrendering%20to%20police%20with%20their%20nine-month-old%20baby%20in%20his%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22hjeeicu%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhjeeicu_himanta-biswa-sarma_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20meets%20family%20members%20of%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20triple%20murder%20case%2C%20in%20Golaghat%20on%20W