0next%20meeting%20for%20August%2025%20and%2026%2C%20in%20Mumbai.%20At%20this%20meeting%2C%20the%20alliance%20had%20earlier%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20finalise%20the%20names%20for%20its%20coordination%20committee%2C%20joint%20secretariat%20and%20other%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20will%20be%20hosted%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fnational-politics%2Fnext-india-meeting-in-mumbai-on-august-25-26-1241348.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20newspaper%20quoted%20an%20opposition%20party%20leader%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20dates%20will%20be%20finalised%20after%20the%20parliament%20session%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20constitute%20%E2%80%9CINDIA%20committees%E2%80%9D%20for%20campaigns%2C%20media%20and%20agitation%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20call%20it%20sub-committees%20but%20INDIA%20committees%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Bengaluru%20meeting%20on%20July%2018%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%20will%20be%20set%20up%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%A6A%20central%20secretariat%20will%20also%20be%20set%20up%20for%20campaign%20management%20and%20joint%20rallies%20and%20action%20there.%20The%20secretariat%20will%20work%20out%20of%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%20will%20be%20representative%20of%20all%20parties%20and%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20electoral%20and%20political%20strategy%20including%20communication%20points%2C%20joint%20rallies%2C%20seat-sharing%20and%20other%20such%20aspects%20of%20the%20opposition%20front.%20Kharge%20added%20that%20the%20front%20will%20choose%20its%20president%20and%20conv