9CFor%20many%20people%20with%20neurodiversity%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20go%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20work%20in%20an%20office%20environment.%20We%20outsource%20work%20from%20factories%20for%20them%20so%20they%20can%20work%20from%20home%20with%20ease.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20supply%20the%20materials%20needed%20to%20make%20boxes%20or%20packaging%20work%2C%20so%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20the%20stress%20of%20working%20in%20a%20factory%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20NGO%20has%20helped%20over%2050%20people%20secure%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20discovery%20of%20the%20excellent%20artistic%20talents%20of%20neurodivergent%20people%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20help%20artists%20find%20a%20platform%20by%20conducting%20exhibitions%2C%20both%20online%20and%20offline.%20This%20way%2C%20they%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20promote%20their%20work%20and%20get%20recognition.%20We%20also%20help%20them%20get%20orders%3B%20for%20instance%2C%20during%20Diwali%2C%20we%20try%20to%20secure%20orders%20for%20specially%20commissioned%20artworks%20of%20Lakhsmi%20and%20Ganesha.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20has%20held%20two%20exhibitions%20so%20far%20and%20raised%20Rs%2010%20Lakh%20showcasing%20the%20artwork%20of%2021%20neurodivergent%20people%20from%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20mentoring%20four%20young%20neurodivergent%20photographers%20and%20helping%20them%20secure%20professional%20assignments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20neurodivergent%20people%20Tarini%20has%20helped%20is%20Aditya%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20who%20works%20with%20Nippon%20Paint%20in%20Gurugram.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20degree%20in%20marketing%20and%20animation%20but%20could%20not%20find%20work.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20land%20an%20internship%20with%20Nippon%2