20I%20decided%20to%20believe%20in%20Aadya.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20believing%20in%20your%20children%20and%20setting%20higher%20goals%20can%20motivate%20them%20a%20lot.%20While%20others%20were%20doubting%20our%20decision%2C%20I%20showed%20Aadya%20utmost%20confidence%20and%20encouraged%20her%20to%20keep%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20she%20successfully%20completed%20the%20EBC%20trek%2C%20she%20did%20not%20understand%20the%20enormity%20of%20what%20she%20had%20done%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age.%20She%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20fun%20activity%2C%20but%20I%20am%20sure%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20she%20will%20understand%20it.%20As%20a%20parent%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20only%20providing%20her%20with%20the%20right%20avenues%20and%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Aadya%E2%80%99s%20diet%2C%20her%20mother%20Mangala%2C%20who%20is%20a%20sports%20nutritionist%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20age%2C%20most%20children%20are%20picky%20eaters.%20Before%20the%20trek%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20she%20had%20energy-rich%20food%20to%20handle%20the%20physical%20activity.%20Besides%20proteins%20and%20nutrients%2C%20we%20also%20let%20her%20eat%20whatever%20she%20likes%20based%20on%20her%20taste%20preferences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20keep%20her%20fueled%20and%20help%20her%20recover%20faster%20from%20training%2C%20we%20added%20fruit-and-nut%20milkshakes%2C%20grilled%20cheese%20and%20vegetable%20sandwiches%2C%20omelettes%20and%20homemade%20high-calorie%20desserts%20to%20her%20regular%20South%20Indian%20ovo-vegetarian%20diet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Polley%20Polley%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Eup%20the%20Kilimanjaro%20Peak%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20around%20two%20months%20of%20training%2C%20the%20father-daughter%20duo%20flew%20to%20Africa%20on%20June%2013%2C%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadya%20says%20that%20while%20climbing%20to%20