nvironmental%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20do%20their%20bit%20to%20tackle%20the%20growing%20plastic%20problem%2C%20siblings%20Rishabh%20and%20Rohan%20started%20Qudrat%2C%20a%20Kerala-based%20startup%20that%20creates%20biodegradable%20tableware%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277852%2Fthoosan-edible-plates-spoons-tableware-from-kerala-biodegradable-wheat-rice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20rice%20bran%2C%20rice%20husk%2C%20and%20rice%20straw%20%E2%80%94%20to%20replace%20paper%20and%20plastic%20disposable%20tableware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-2-1690203447.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20Qudrat%2C%20siblings%20creates%20biodegradable%20serveware%20from%20agricultural%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20rice%20bran%2C%20rice%20husk%2C%20and%20rice%20straw.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-2-1690203447.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-2-1690203447-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-2-1690203447-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-2-1690203447-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-2-1690203447-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324932%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20Qudrat%2C%20siblings%20create%20biodegradable%20tableware%20from%20agricultural%20waste%2C%20such%20as%20rice%20bran%2C%20rice%20husk%2C%20and%20rice%20straw.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20products%20have%20found%20customers%20not%20only%20in%20Indian%20metros%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20but%20also%20in%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20and%20the%20Northeastern%20states%20of%20Mizoram%20and%20Nagaland.%20Apart%20from%20India%2C%20the%20siblings%20have%20buyers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Rishabh%20says%2C%20they%20sold%20about%2025%2C000%20units%20of%20plates%2C%20straws%2C%20spoons%2C%20and%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20quest%20to%20find%20a%20better%20substitute%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20dropping%20out%20of%20Chartered%20Accountancy%2C%20he%20got%20into%20his%20family%20business%20of%20selling%20motorcycles.%20The%20BCom%20graduate%20continued%20the%20automobile%20franchise%20business%20till%202020%20before%20founding%20his%20own%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20collect%20husk%20and%20rice%20grain%20from%20mills%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20and%20straw%20from%20farmers%20across%20Kerala%20belt%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690