%20satellite%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20also%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20build%20completely%20new%20hardware%20and%20we%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20build%20and%20test%20it.%20COVID%20further%20slowed%20us%20down.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20work%20on%20our%20hardware%20at%20the%20pace%20we%20usually%20do.%20We%20also%20faced%20supply%20issues%20which%20delayed%20our%20launches.%20However%2C%20we%20kept%20ourselves%20motivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Pixxel%20raised%20%2436%20million%20from%20investors%20including%20Google.%20From%20four%20people%20in%202019%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20now%20grown%20to%20a%20big%20team%20of%20147%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAwais%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20now%2C%20has%20realised%20a%20few%20dreams%20he%20saw%20as%20a%20child.%20He%20is%20working%20on%20cutting-edge%20space%20technology%20and%20has%20sent%20satellites%20into%20orbit.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20still%20have%20many%20more%20dreams.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20travel%20and%20live%20on%20a%20colony%20in%20space.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689947214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel7-1689934892.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324699%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Space%20enthusiasts%20Awais%20Ahmed%20and%20Kshitij%20Khandelwal%20started%20Pixxel%20%E2%80%94%20a%20startup%20that%20works%20on%20building%20and%20launching%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20satellites%20to%20combat%20climate%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Raip