ed%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooking%20classes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%20She%20says%20she%20has%20trained%20at%20least%201%2C000%20foreigners%20from%20Italy%2C%20Russia%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Poland%2C%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20pursuit%20of%20a%20better%20life%20for%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%2C%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20Rajasthan%20village%2C%20was%20happily%20married%20to%20a%20hotel%20manager.%20One%20night%2C%20she%20grew%20worried%20when%20her%20husband%20didn%E2%80%99t%20return%20from%20work.%20However%2C%20he%20called%20to%20reassure%20her%20that%20he%20would%20be%20back%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20asked%20me%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20daal%20paratha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flat%20bread%20stuffed%20with%20black%20lentils).%20I%20had%20kept%20the%20filling%20and%20dough%20ready%20the%20next%20morning.%20But%20then%20I%20received%20a%20call%20and%20my%20life%20was%20shattered%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more.%20My%20husband%20was%20murdered%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20for%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CLosing%20him%20was%20so%20painful.%20I%20had%20lost%20all%20hope%20to%20live%2C%20but%20I%20had%20two%20sons%20to%20look%20after.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%E2%80%99s%20sons%20were%20aged%20five%20and%20seven%20years%20when%20her%20husband%20died%20in%202001.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20even%20arrange%20for%20%3Cem%3Epagdi%20dastoor%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Rajasthani%20tradition%20wherein%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20dead%20are%20passed%20to%20their%20son).%20We%20survived%20on%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20mirch%20roti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbread%20with%20chilly%20and%20salt)%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv